OL,5, Charities and campaigners are urging   
OL,6, ministers to set up an inquiry into the
OL,7, treatment of unaccompanied children    
OL,8, seeking asylum in the UK.              
OL,10,FThe call comes after an official report
OL,11,Fsaid basic checks to keep children safe
OL,12,Fin asylum hotels were not carried out. 
OL,14,FIn an open letter, the groups highlight
OL,15,Fthe "appalling revelation" some        
OL,16,Fchildren were asked to play a game to  
OL,17,Fguess who would be in foster care next.
OL,19,FThe Home Office said the welfare of the
OL,20,Fchildren was an "utmost priority".     
